==Russian==
===Etymology===
From [[сей]] + [[час]], "this hour".

===Adverb===
'''сейчас''' (sejčás)

# [[now]], [[at present]]
# [[presently]], [[immediately]], [[at once]]
# [[just]] now

===Synonyms===
*[[теперь]]

